jgame.controller

Class ConstantMovementController

  • java.lang.Object
    • jgame.controller.ConstantMovementController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Controller
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GParallax.GTiledSprite.ScrollController

    public class ConstantMovementController
extends java.lang.Object
implements Controller
    A simple controller that continuously moves the target at a constant velocity.
    Author:
    William Chargin

        Parameters:

        Returns:

        Creates a ConstantMotionController according to the given polar vector (r, θ ) (or, equivalently, (v, θ)). The generated controller will cause the target to move at the given speed in the given direction, with the given damping.
